{"id":"808361484823461888","type":"text","timestamp":1770913586,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/808361484823461888","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://theenvioussoul.tumblr.com/post/808284908342706176/i-hate-being-so-tall-sometimes-i-just-want\">theenvioussoul</a>:</p><blockquote><p>I hate being so tall sometimes. I just want someone taller than me to pin me against the wall with a hand beside my head and do that slight lean towards, staring right into my eyes.</p><p><span class=\"npf_color_joey\"><b>&hellip;oughhh I WANT IT SO BADDD</b></span></p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"theenvioussoul"},"post":{"id":"808284908342706176"}}],"baseline_notes":17,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}